Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:20.41,1:30:25.41,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  真正的所在
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:25.91,1:30:31.08,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  這就是愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:31.33,1:30:36.47,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在冰冷的黑暗中  伸手尋找溫暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:36.63,1:30:42.39,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天  奇跡也一定會發生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:44.97,1:30:55.30,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic 如果有愛 就絕對有具體的形式
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:55.82,1:31:06.33,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic 現在 在我手中 有誕生的氣息
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:06.58,1:31:14.59,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是精神飽滿  也不能   太過勉強
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:14.96,1:31:19.88,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  把些微的勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:20.38,1:31:31.06,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  凝聚起來  培育茁壯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.67,0:00:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,流動的水沒有形狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.17,0:00:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漂流的風找不到蹤跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.07,0:00:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任何案件的推理都取決於心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.97,0:00:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝大家新年快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.57,0:00:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正逢千禧年 獻上2小時特別節目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.07,0:00:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.64,0:00:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.40,0:00:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.44,0:00:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.67,0:01:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,九局下半場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.57,0:01:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前比數3比2 中日隊領先1分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.07,0:01:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們用來壓制對手的王牌小松
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.47,0:01:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經投出兩好球 跑者滑向二壘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.37,0:02:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉他了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.07,0:02:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四發都打中了身體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.97,0:02:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢伙不見閻王也難了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.17,0:02:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑影計畫師叶才三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.57,0:02:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在也變成一堆海草了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.97,0:02:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.17,0:02:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一帶的潮流來得特別快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.67,0:02:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在屍體浮起來以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.67,0:02:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會被魚吃到肚子裡去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.07,0:02:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.77,0:02:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼樣也沒有必要把他殺了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.07,0:02:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.97,0:02:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不過是殺了一個銀行職員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.17,0:02:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就嚷著要去自首
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.27,0:02:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能放著不管呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.27,0:02:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再說 警察都已經知道他的長相了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.37,0:02:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些都不重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.77,0:02:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些錢怎麼處置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.37,0:02:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.97,0:02:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那四億裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.97,0:02:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有三億的號碼都是照號碼排的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.67,0:02:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怕個屁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.47,0:02:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們兄弟這次幹了這麼一大筆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.07,0:02:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在只要等風聲過去就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.77,0:02:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.37,0:03:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個就算是我們給你的餞別禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.07,0:03:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別怪我們無情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.07,0:03:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.17,0:03:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第20年的殺意 交響樂號連續殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.27,0:03:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唱片啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.27,0:03:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}這裏指的是以前的那種密紋唱片,而不是CD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.37,0:03:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這題的答案一定是唱片錯不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.47,0:03:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼東西錯不了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.87,0:03:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.97,0:03:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.77,0:03:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.77,0:03:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好康道相報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.57,0:03:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.87,0:03:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昭和年代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.87,0:03:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大部分的日本人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.57,0:03:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都會保留有一件重要的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.97,0:03:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在還有這樣東西嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.17,0:03:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要是現在還擁有這種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.77,0:03:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幾乎完全絕跡的寶貴物品的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.47,0:03:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就可以參加...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.37,0:03:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,往下看 看下面的那一段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.17,0:03:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別吵嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.67,0:03:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前10位幸運朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.77,0:04:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將獲邀免費參加小笠原海豚旅行團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.07,0:04:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸 我們就帶著唱片去看看嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.07,0:04:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定現在去還來得及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.97,0:04:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你也想看海豚對不對？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.87,0:04:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 柯南？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.57,0:04:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以啦 反正這個假期你也是閒著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.47,0:04:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要去這個什麼旅行團啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.67,0:04:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再說 妳的答案根本就錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.47,0:04:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是唱片的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.57,0:04:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他根本不會注明什麼日本人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.67,0:04:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你說答案是什麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.67,0:04:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.47,0:04:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然是現在的日本人消失的武士道精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.77,0:04:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西要怎麼帶去啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.67,0:04:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再說 不管從前或是現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.27,0:04:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都沒有什麼武士道精神啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.37,0:04:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那有可能是溜溜球或者是喇叭褲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.67,0:04:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然也有可能是紅茶香菇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.77,0:04:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CD 化妝品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.57,0:04:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.37,0:04:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得「圍巾蜥蜴」怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.47,0:05:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在以前啊 可是很流行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.47,0:05:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.37,0:05:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.27,0:05:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這題的答案會不會是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.87,0:05:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 正確答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.07,0:05:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在請三位上船吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.77,0:05:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.77,0:05:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.97,0:05:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南說的答案果然對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.17,0:05:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是碰巧猜到的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.37,0:05:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下組來賓 請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.07,0:05:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.37,0:05:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還好我還保存了以前的錢幣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.47,0:05:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快把錢收起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.77,0:05:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓後面的人看見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.37,0:05:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔也太小氣了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.57,0:05:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你儘管放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.07,0:05:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.77,0:05:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不是說要就拿得出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.77,0:05:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.57,0:05:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是魔術方塊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.77,0:05:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.47,0:05:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們答錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.57,0:05:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.67,0:05:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 下一組請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.77,0:05:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.67,0:05:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這艘船還真是壯觀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.07,0:05:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得好興奮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.47,0:05:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜三位答對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.07,0:05:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是專為這次旅行團製作的手冊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.27,0:05:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.77,0:06:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 請問我們是第幾個答對的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.07,0:06:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們一共有三位成員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.97,0:06:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了這位小朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.37,0:06:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來應該還會有一個人的名額
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.17,0:06:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還好被我們趕上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.67,0:06:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太幸運了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.07,0:06:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個旅行團只招待10個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.47,0:06:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這艘船未免太大了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.77,0:06:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 快來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.37,0:06:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.97,0:06:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像飯店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.67,0:06:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搭這種船去小笠原倒是不錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.87,0:06:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位先生恭喜你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.67,0:06:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.77,0:06:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生一行人一共三個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.47,0:06:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問你們是家人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.07,0:06:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.27,0:06:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就請住115號房 裡面有兩張床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.27,0:06:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生 我想向你請教一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.27,0:06:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問負責策劃這次旅行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.97,0:06:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那位古川大先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.77,0:06:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是已經上船了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.17,0:06:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.87,0:06:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他讓我們搭乘這麼豪華的船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.17,0:06:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少應該向他道謝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.37,0:06:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我們還沒見過他的人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.77,0:06:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連你們都還沒見過啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.27,0:06:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 其實從他預定這艘船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.77,0:07:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以至於選擇搭乘旅客的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.77,0:07:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是利用電話跟我們聯絡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.07,0:07:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就連包船的費用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.47,0:07:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也事先匯到銀行去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.67,0:07:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想 他一定是在小笠原那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.77,0:07:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等待上船的乘客吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.27,0:07:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.57,0:07:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 這位先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.17,0:07:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以請教您尊姓大名嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.67,0:07:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.67,0:07:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不瞞你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.97,0:07:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我就是毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.27,0:07:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過去曾經任職警視廳搜查一課
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.17,0:07:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在是壞小孩看了都怕的名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.27,0:07:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.77,0:07:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鮫崎刑警組長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.17,0:07:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我早就不做警察了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.47,0:07:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這個老傢伙在兩年前就已經從警界退休了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.57,0:07:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.67,0:07:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭 你真是越長越漂亮了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.37,0:07:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是妳怎麼會來這裡呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.77,0:07:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過就是想出來看看大海嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.57,0:08:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為 今天可是特別的日子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.27,0:08:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特別的日子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.37,0:08:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙 10年前就不幹警察了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.07,0:08:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會忘記這個日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.07,0:08:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是情有可原的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.97,0:08:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.57,0:08:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你那漂亮老婆怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.77,0:08:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在該不會還在搞分居吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.77,0:08:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還真給你猜對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.77,0:08:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就不用管那個女人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.27,0:08:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.67,0:08:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.57,0:08:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.77,0:08:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 沒什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.27,0:08:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,印章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.37,0:08:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的東西掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.77,0:08:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.97,0:08:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.67,0:08:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡 不謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.67,0:08:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳幫他撿了東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.27,0:08:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛還要跟他道謝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.77,0:08:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個你就不用管了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.97,0:08:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.97,0:09:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫我有什麼事啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.37,0:09:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我等你很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.07,0:09:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 過去喝一杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.07,0:09:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位客人 我來幫你提行李吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.57,0:09:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.97,0:09:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位先生 請問只有您一個人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.57,0:09:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.67,0:09:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了那個小弟弟不算呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.97,0:09:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他剛好是第10個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.47,0:09:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是最後的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.47,0:09:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 我們現在就可以開船了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.17,0:09:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,預計的時間都已經過了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.47,0:09:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.47,0:09:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想 第一個到這裡的那位老先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.57,0:09:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說他忘了帶一樣東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.37,0:09:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他已經離開了 到現在還沒回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.67,0:09:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說的那位老先生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.17,0:09:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實剛才已經來過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.87,0:09:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說在晚餐前要先睡一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.97,0:09:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還特別交待我們不要去叫醒他呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.57,0:09:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.57,0:09:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.17,0:09:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要這10個名額都到就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.67,0:09:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就麻煩你請其他的人回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.07,0:09:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.17,0:09:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 這位先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.27,0:10:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您是107號房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.27,0:10:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.17,0:10:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你留步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.67,0:10:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.87,0:10:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是不是在什麼地方見過呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.27,0:10:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 你大概認錯人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.57,0:10:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天可是第一次見到你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.97,0:10:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會是以為你找到了哪個通緝犯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.67,0:10:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鮫崎組長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.27,0:10:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托你們的福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.17,0:10:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一路上可以放一百二十個心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.57,0:10:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.07,0:10:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.87,0:10:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一位是前刑警 一位是偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.97,0:10:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加上你們兩位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.77,0:10:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就有三位鎮船之寶了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.07,0:10:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三位？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.57,0:10:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了我們兩個之外還有一個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.47,0:10:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 還有另外一位偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.27,0:10:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是外表完全看不出來就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.37,0:10:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.17,0:10:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠利用交響樂二號為各位旅客服務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.27,0:10:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次非常感謝大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.77,0:10:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本船現在即將出航
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.67,0:10:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,預計明天早上抵達我們的目的地 小笠原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.17,0:10:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請盡情享受這段船上的時光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.27,0:11:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the king of the world
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.97,0:11:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說一直想親口說說這句話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.37,0:11:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個傢伙電影看多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.47,0:11:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是船沉了怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.17,0:11:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是觸霉頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.97,0:11:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看見夕陽染紅的汪洋大海啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.87,0:11:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼前有這種壯觀的景致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.67,0:11:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是誰都會像她一樣想大聲呐喊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.57,0:11:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種感覺真舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.47,0:11:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大海很美對不對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.67,0:12:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 不開心的事情全都不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.57,0:12:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.87,0:12:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大海永遠都會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.87,0:12:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隱藏一切是非善惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.47,0:12:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不論是痛苦的回憶還是不安的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.77,0:12:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.37,0:12:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屍體也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.57,0:12:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才說屍體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.27,0:12:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.77,0:12:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說了些奇怪的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.07,0:12:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我父親過去就是死在海裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.87,0:12:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.27,0:12:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.87,0:12:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說起來我們都得心懷感激
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.77,0:12:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了那個叫古川的人策劃了這次的旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.27,0:12:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道這個人是誰喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.07,0:12:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才 我不是撿了一個印章嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.57,0:12:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛好被我看到上面刻了古川兩個字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.57,0:12:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你也看到了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.37,0:12:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以剛才妳才會向那個傢伙道謝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.47,0:12:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.87,0:12:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以啦 你們看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.97,0:12:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才拿著那個印章的人就是古川先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.37,0:13:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一定是想在晚餐的時候再表明身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.27,0:13:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好給大家一個意外的驚喜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.57,0:13:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.37,0:13:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才問過那個人的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.27,0:13:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他明明說他姓龜田啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.07,0:13:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.77,0:13:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.87,0:13:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃晚飯的時間到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.47,0:13:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.27,0:13:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是那位鼎鼎大名的沉睡的小五郎啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.87,0:13:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.87,0:13:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我真是有眼不識泰山了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.87,0:13:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.67,0:13:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先到房間裡去躺著好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.67,0:13:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.67,0:13:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼還是這麼怕坐船啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.47,0:13:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要為您倒杯酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.37,0:13:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 麻煩你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.97,0:13:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老實說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.97,0:13:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼大一艘船就我們這幾個客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.37,0:13:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是有點冷清啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.27,0:13:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您說得沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.17,0:13:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在就算把那兩位在房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.77,0:13:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裡面休息的客人加起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.07,0:13:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過才11名乘客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.67,0:13:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是把我算進去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.47,0:13:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說的這兩位是另一名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.57,0:13:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟老先生嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.67,0:13:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.57,0:13:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說的這位老人家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.97,0:14:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在樓下的時候也剛好看到過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.77,0:14:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看他不怎麼愛說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.17,0:14:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可知道他是做什麼的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.57,0:14:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說他是一位海洋研究學家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.37,0:14:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他好像叫做叶才三先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.87,0:14:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他叫叶才三？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.67,0:14:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙住在哪一個房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.47,0:14:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他住101號房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.57,0:14:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叶才三啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.17,0:14:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這名字好像在哪兒聽過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.97,0:14:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 你忘了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.17,0:14:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是我跟你以前一起負責追查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.37,0:14:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那四億元強盜殺人案件的主謀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.47,0:14:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑影計畫師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.97,0:14:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叶才三本人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.67,0:15:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬能鑰匙帶了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.37,0:15:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.47,0:15:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.47,0:15:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.47,0:15:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定隨時都會攜帶槍械
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.77,0:15:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一開門 就立刻退下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.67,0:15:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.17,0:15:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.17,0:15:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.27,0:15:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,門打開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.27,0:15:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.77,0:15:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.27,0:15:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.87,0:15:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡根本不像有人住過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.67,0:15:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他真的住在這間房間吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.77,0:15:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 這點絕對不會錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.87,0:15:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.47,0:15:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到下面去找一找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.07,0:15:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛利啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.57,0:15:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這上面就交給你負責了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.97,0:15:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.67,0:16:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.57,0:16:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在這邊吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.27,0:16:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經看過信了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.47,0:16:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他如果不在房裡頭的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.47,0:16:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定他會在甲板上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.47,0:16:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這102號房是誰住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.67,0:16:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那位偵探的房間啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.07,0:16:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他從上船以後呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.47,0:16:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就一直待在房裡沒有出來過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.47,0:16:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.47,0:16:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.17,0:16:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.27,0:16:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾您一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.37,0:16:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.27,0:16:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我來叫叫看好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.07,0:16:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裡面的人聽著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.97,0:16:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在裡面對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.47,0:16:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.47,0:16:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒別的辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.17,0:16:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就幫我把門打開好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.87,0:16:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.07,0:17:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個到底有完沒完啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.97,0:17:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.77,0:17:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們怎麼會也來這裡啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.27,0:17:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你又為什麼來了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.37,0:17:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑影計畫師？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.07,0:17:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,經你這麼一說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.37,0:17:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我倒想起小時候聽我老爸提起過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.37,0:17:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前的確是有這麼一號人物耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.97,0:17:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的本名叫做叶才三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.17,0:17:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20年前曾經爆發一件四億元強盜殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.87,0:17:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是那件強盜殺人案的主謀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.17,0:17:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的計畫詳盡周密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.97,0:17:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再加上無人匹敵的技巧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.07,0:17:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弄得警方一團迷霧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.87,0:17:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人稱「黑影計畫師」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.97,0:17:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一向獨來獨往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.27,0:17:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯完案通常立刻改換搭檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.37,0:17:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯案過程中不傷害任何人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.87,0:17:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一向是他最大的特色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.87,0:17:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.97,0:17:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯下20年前那件案子的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.97,0:17:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他終於失手殺了一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.47,0:17:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從那次事情之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.67,0:17:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就沒有人再見過他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.17,0:17:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是說這麼一號人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.17,0:18:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就睡在我的隔壁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.47,0:18:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過他早就金蟬脫殼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.07,0:18:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在鮫崎組長正在找他呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.07,0:18:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這很奇怪耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.67,0:18:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得那個傢伙明明已經死了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.27,0:18:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,案子爆發之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.67,0:18:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一件留有槍痕跟血跡的衣服被打上了岸邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.27,0:18:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是我老爸告訴我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.07,0:18:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他根本還沒有死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.87,0:18:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那件上衣只是他擺脫警方追查的陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.47,0:18:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像他那種人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.07,0:18:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不可能這麼輕易就死在那種地方的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.37,0:18:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小兄弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.27,0:18:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本來以為這時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.37,0:18:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一定在哪個地方跟他那群兄弟高興地數鈔票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.07,0:18:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.67,0:18:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他竟然也會坐上這艘船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.27,0:18:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.17,0:18:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那件案子五年前就過了時效了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.97,0:18:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到他又能怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.67,0:18:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.57,0:18:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你難道忘了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.97,0:18:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺人案的時效是15年沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.47,0:18:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是民法規定20年之內都還是法律追訴期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.17,0:18:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當事人要他們還錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.77,0:18:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就一定得還才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.97,0:18:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.57,0:18:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾 被警方通緝的叶才三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.57,0:18:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經過了法律追訴期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.67,0:19:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過他那三個兄弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.37,0:19:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有脫離法律追訴期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.97,0:19:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們只要能逮到叶才三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.57,0:19:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問出那些兄弟的下落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.17,0:19:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該多少能把錢給找回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.37,0:19:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是呢 說不定他那三個兄弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.07,0:19:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早就已經混到這艘船上來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.07,0:19:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.17,0:19:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就等到了小笠原之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.77,0:19:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再跟那邊的警察一起找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.27,0:19:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡一片汪洋大海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.27,0:19:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算他們想逃也沒那麼容易啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.77,0:19:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.67,0:19:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒有時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.97,0:19:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說過今天是個特別的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.67,0:19:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當初那件案子就發生在20年前的明天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.67,0:19:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過了午夜12點之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.57,0:19:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們三個就可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.37,0:19:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無罪一身輕地告別逃亡生涯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.67,0:19:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說再過兩個多小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.87,0:19:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法律追訴期就過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.57,0:19:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,服部 你也來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.87,0:19:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭 好久不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.27,0:19:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這麼巧呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.67,0:19:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來你也坐上這艘船了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.07,0:19:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 我本來睡得正香呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.27,0:20:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大叔卻把我硬生生地叫起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.47,0:20:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 和葉也一起來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.87,0:20:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個女人幹嘛要出現在這裡啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.37,0:20:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她又不是我的什麼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.87,0:20:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們才不像你們整天膩在一起呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.67,0:20:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.37,0:20:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 我是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.77,0:20:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們這對父女感情還真是不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.57,0:20:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要你雞婆啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.87,0:20:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鮫崎叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.17,0:20:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們找到了那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.37,0:20:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑影什麼的叔叔了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.37,0:20:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.57,0:20:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正打算現在跟毛利重新找過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.07,0:20:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 我們就先到下面的餐廳去好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.97,0:20:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.47,0:20:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也要在這裡幫忙找人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.97,0:20:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.17,0:20:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在船上潛伏了這麼一號危險人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.07,0:20:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然要丟下我一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.07,0:20:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.57,0:20:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我等你過來 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.87,0:20:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.97,0:20:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.37,0:20:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我等你 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.47,0:20:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.87,0:20:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是哪裡不舒服啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.77,0:20:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鮫崎組長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.57,0:21:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 我沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.37,0:21:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 依我看呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.77,0:21:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就從上面依序往下找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.57,0:21:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.07,0:21:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我真的沒想到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.77,0:21:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,服部你竟然也會喜歡海豚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.47,0:21:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海豚？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.17,0:21:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.07,0:21:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是看了報紙上的廣告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.47,0:21:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才坐上這艘船的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.87,0:21:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.07,0:21:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以會坐上這艘船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.87,0:21:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為一封奇怪的信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.27,0:21:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一封奇怪的信？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.77,0:21:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.57,0:21:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在一個禮拜以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.77,0:21:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我收到一封署名給我的信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.57,0:21:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說是要我到小笠原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.37,0:21:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到那裡幫他查一件案子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.87,0:21:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那封信裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.77,0:21:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還事先附上了他委託我查案的十萬元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.27,0:21:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十萬元？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.47,0:21:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.37,0:21:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我覺得很奇怪的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.57,0:21:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那十萬塊全都是過去的紙鈔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.57,0:21:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有寫明寄件人的地址
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.67,0:21:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寄件人是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.37,0:21:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面寫著一個叫古川大的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.57,0:21:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是古川啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.97,0:21:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 你們認識這個傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.67,0:21:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這是什麼話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.37,0:22:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次招待我們來旅行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.27,0:22:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那位叫古川的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.27,0:22:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 這我倒不知道耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.37,0:22:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他只在信上寫說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.07,0:22:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把鈔票拿給他們看就能上船了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.57,0:22:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 平次哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.97,0:22:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是以偵探的名義被邀請來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.17,0:22:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這個人查案子向來不收錢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.27,0:22:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就想見了人再把錢還給他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.07,0:22:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才上了這艘船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.77,0:22:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然囉 也想知道要辦什麼案子啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.07,0:22:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這也太巧合了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.87,0:22:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到我們會坐上同一艘船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.37,0:22:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我有先打過電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.97,0:22:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我到羽田的時候 工藤...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.27,0:22:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不...不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.17,0:22:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就想也找毛利大叔一起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.17,0:22:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.67,0:22:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都沒有人接電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.67,0:22:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你一定是在我們出門後才打的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.37,0:22:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之呢 我們還是見到面就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.17,0:22:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下大野狼還是大野狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.67,0:22:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偵探還是偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.77,0:22:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一樣沒有改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.77,0:22:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧? 小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.37,0:22:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 你就是他們說的偵探囉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.27,0:22:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你這麼年輕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.07,0:22:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.27,0:22:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.17,0:22:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到那個叫叶才三的人沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.47,0:23:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.07,0:23:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們現在好像還在找耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.57,0:23:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我借你用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.07,0:23:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 我用完就還你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.47,0:23:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有需要就告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.87,0:23:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們幾個一起去休息室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.27,0:23:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩撲克牌怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.87,0:23:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好是好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.77,0:23:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是沒有牌啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.47,0:23:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.57,0:23:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己有帶撲克牌來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.77,0:23:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們要不要一起玩啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.07,0:23:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正現在也是閒著嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.47,0:23:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.27,0:23:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 都沒看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.07,0:23:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 他消失到哪兒去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.17,0:23:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 只剩下一個小時了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.17,0:23:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.97,0:23:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會放棄的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.97,0:23:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到這件案子到最後一分鐘為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.87,0:23:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也絕不死心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.27,0:23:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鮫崎組長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.87,0:23:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就再找一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.77,0:23:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.97,0:24:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就再徹徹底底找一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.27,0:24:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.77,0:24:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.67,0:24:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是 Full House
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.87,0:24:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 搞什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.77,0:24:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼又被妳贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.47,0:24:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我們再來玩一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.97,0:24:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後輸的人就跟鯨井先生交換
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.57,0:24:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.37,0:24:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道現在幾點了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.27,0:24:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還差5分就12點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.37,0:24:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.27,0:24:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好像一直很在意時間啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:27.17,0:24:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有什麼事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:29.77,0:24:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為明天是一個很重要的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.67,0:24:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們看 我有A和9兩對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.07,0:24:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你怎麼又贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:37.47,0:24:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來又是我輸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.47,0:24:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 現在輪到鯨井先生玩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:41.67,0:24:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 妳可要手下留情啊 小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.97,0:24:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說重要的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.77,0:24:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是女朋友的忌日吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:57.67,0:24:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你那杯雞尾酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:59.67,0:25:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不正是血腥瑪麗嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:02.57,0:25:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:03.37,0:25:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天是你最愛的女人消香玉殞的日子吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:07.57,0:25:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:12.47,0:25:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 找到了沒？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:16.47,0:25:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到處都沒找到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:18.87,0:25:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那位以前做刑警的大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:20.27,0:25:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡了啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:21.77,0:25:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說他要堅持到最後一分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:24.87,0:25:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:25.77,0:25:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要喝點什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:27.17,0:25:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我杯水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:28.77,0:25:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:29.67,0:25:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:30.77,0:25:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看我也差不多該離開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:33.17,0:25:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要先走一步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:35.27,0:25:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:36.37,0:25:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那這副牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:37.27,0:25:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待會兒我們擺到盒子裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:39.17,0:25:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再直接送去房間給妳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:41.57,0:25:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 那就要麻煩你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:44.37,0:25:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問 我喝的這杯多少錢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:46.07,0:25:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也幫我算一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:48.67,0:25:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 我的錢包呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:51.47,0:25:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這該不會是你的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:53.67,0:25:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:55.27,0:25:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到它掉在走廊上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:56.67,0:25:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就順手撿了起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:58.57,0:26:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託 我沒有拿你裡面的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:02.37,0:26:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:03.27,0:26:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是慎重起見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:08.67,0:26:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鯨井先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:09.47,0:26:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也要離開了啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:10.97,0:26:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我去上個廁所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:12.57,0:26:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們先休息一會兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:14.27,0:26:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:42.17,0:26:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間已經過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:44.57,0:26:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不能夠碰這件案子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:47.77,0:26:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真要說起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:48.77,0:26:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在兩年前就辭了刑警的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:51.37,0:26:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早就沒這個資格了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:54.97,0:26:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,組長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:57.07,0:26:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在還可以點酒喝嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:59.47,0:27:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以 沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:02.27,0:27:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我一杯啤酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:03.67,0:27:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:11.37,0:27:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了 組長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:15.17,0:27:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:16.87,0:27:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 毛利 我們來喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:19.37,0:27:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:20.07,0:27:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天喝它個不醉不歸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:22.07,0:27:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天喝的全算我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:24.47,0:27:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算那是他過去負責追查的案子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:27.67,0:27:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也太投入了一點吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:32.77,0:27:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,組長 說起來你以前還是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:36.07,0:27:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的是什麼聲音？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:37.87,0:27:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是從甲板上傳來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:40.67,0:27:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是槍聲！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:41.77,0:27:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛利 現在幾點？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:43.27,0:27:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,12點08分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:54.67,0:27:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,旗子...旗子著火了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:58.87,0:28:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才是什麼聲音啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:00.57,0:28:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到一聲很像煙火的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:03.77,0:28:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:05.07,0:28:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你認為這純粹是個惡作劇嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:06.77,0:28:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 你看看那裡 服部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:11.17,0:28:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:12.87,0:28:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那張一萬元紙鈔上寫了字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:16.27,0:28:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可別碰那把刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:18.07,0:28:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這是對誰說？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:19.77,0:28:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是門外漢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:21.47,0:28:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:22.67,0:28:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以拿個塑膠袋來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:24.27,0:28:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:27.17,0:28:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你隨時都把這個帶在身上啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:29.17,0:28:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經養成習慣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:31.27,0:28:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面都寫了些什麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:34.47,0:28:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海神波賽頓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:36.67,0:28:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又賦予了我生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:38.87,0:28:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的影子也將再度甦醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:42.27,0:28:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鯨井先生...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:43.97,0:28:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:47.07,0:28:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他果然....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:52.87,0:28:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還活著啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:55.67,0:28:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼聲音啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:56.57,0:28:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:57.27,0:28:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼事了？ 怎麼有爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:59.37,0:29:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船長 船尾發生爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:01.47,0:29:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,動力機關停止 立刻滅火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:03.27,0:29:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,動力機關停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:06.17,0:29:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:07.77,0:29:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次是船尾發生了爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:09.87,0:29:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼東西著火啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:13.37,0:29:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是放置緊急用救生梯的箱子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:17.57,0:29:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會發生這種事呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:22.07,0:29:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:23.37,0:29:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人 有個人著火了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:35.27,0:29:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 全部燒焦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:39.47,0:29:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下根本無從得知正確的死亡時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:42.27,0:29:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟這具焦屍是誰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:44.07,0:29:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 說不定眼前這具屍體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:46.57,0:29:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個從船上消失的叶才三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:49.17,0:29:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:50.97,0:29:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 還沒詳細查明之前都很難說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:54.07,0:29:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在想啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:54.97,0:29:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人會不會是蟹江先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:57.77,0:29:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:59.17,0:30:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看他手上戴的手錶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:01.97,0:30:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得我今天問他時間的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:04.27,0:30:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他手上戴著的就是那隻金子打造的手錶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:07.77,0:30:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,經你這麼一說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:09.97,0:30:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然屍體燒得難以辨認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:12.67,0:30:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這毛衣的確是他穿的那一件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:15.07,0:30:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得褲子也是這條沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:18.17,0:30:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會 蟹江先生為什麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:22.57,0:30:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過還真是好笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:24.87,0:30:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼好笑?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:27.07,0:30:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 你們看他的姿勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:30.57,0:30:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他特地彎起了手臂和上半身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:33.27,0:30:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就好像他想要向我們炫耀他那隻金表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:36.17,0:30:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:37.97,0:30:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這叫做熱僵硬現象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:39.67,0:30:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屍體遇火的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:41.97,0:30:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骨骼肌肉在熱力的作用之下會產生熱凝固而收縮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:45.87,0:30:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引發熱僵硬現象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:47.67,0:30:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手腳彎曲後的肌肉要比伸展開的肌肉力量大上許多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:52.07,0:30:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以關節部分全都會呈現彎曲狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:55.17,0:30:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所呈現出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:56.27,0:30:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這種有點類似拳擊選手的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:59.87,0:31:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:00.67,0:31:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被火焚燒的屍體都會自然地呈現這個樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:04.77,0:31:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這個樣子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:07.17,0:31:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得最大的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:08.57,0:31:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在於那塊手錶的錶帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:10.17,0:31:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錶帶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:11.17,0:31:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的錶帶有什麼不對啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:14.57,0:31:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自己看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:15.87,0:31:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錶帶都已經鬆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:17.17,0:31:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這有什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:18.27,0:31:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是那個鐵罐當時滾到了屍體附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:21.37,0:31:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想剛才的爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:23.17,0:31:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕就是因為裡面的汽油外漏才會起火爆炸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:27.17,0:31:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然是鐵罐引發的爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:29.37,0:31:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錶帶會鬆也是很自然的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:31.57,0:31:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:32.87,0:31:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原本覆蓋在箱子上面的塑膠布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:35.27,0:31:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該也是當時被炸開的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:36.97,0:31:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塑膠布？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:39.07,0:31:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:39.87,0:31:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟組長之前為了找到叶才三到這裡來的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:43.17,0:31:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面就蓋了張塑膠布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:45.07,0:31:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就跟那張一模一樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:47.37,0:31:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:48.07,0:31:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想當時你們應該有調查過箱子裡面的東西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:51.87,0:31:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 你也看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:53.27,0:31:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塑膠布是從外面被人綁緊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:55.67,0:31:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想不會有傻子笨到躲在裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:58.77,0:32:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再說 蟹江先生絕對不會在這個箱子裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:03.47,0:32:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為 在我回到休息室的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:05.47,0:32:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蟹江先生人還在那裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:08.37,0:32:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說毛利啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:10.57,0:32:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個小夥子他是誰啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:13.07,0:32:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他叫做服部平次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:15.57,0:32:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是大阪府警局本部長的兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:19.17,0:32:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是平藏的兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:20.67,0:32:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難怪會知道這麼多奇奇怪怪的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:23.27,0:32:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們認識啊？ 鮫崎組長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:25.77,0:32:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,何止認識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:26.47,0:32:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是在劍道比賽常常交手過招的劍友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:30.07,0:32:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我根本就不是他的對手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:33.27,0:32:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,服部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:35.27,0:32:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:36.27,0:32:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這具焦屍臉上有個奇怪的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:38.97,0:32:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的東西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:41.67,0:32:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這...這不是橡膠嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:45.67,0:32:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 這種材質叫橡膠樹脂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:50.17,0:32:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡稱橡膠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:52.37,0:32:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在雖然遇熱變形了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:54.17,0:32:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過整形手術中的隆鼻手術常常會使用到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:57.67,0:32:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:59.07,0:33:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來曾經整過形啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:01.17,0:33:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 我想應該錯不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:04.57,0:33:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:06.87,0:33:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用這個蓋住屍體吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:10.07,0:33:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果說這個傢伙曾經去整形過的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:13.37,0:33:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 很有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:15.47,0:33:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是當年搶了銀行四億元的四個歹徒之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:22.27,0:33:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果那具焦屍真的是蟹江先生的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:25.17,0:33:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自從上船以後就跟他交談甚歡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:26.97,0:33:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龜田先生就有可能是他的同夥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:30.67,0:33:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩個都去整形的老朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:32.17,0:33:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼多年不見了自然有很多話要說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:35.87,0:33:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來另外一個就是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:37.87,0:33:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才就一直在我們這群人後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:40.17,0:33:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拼命流汗的那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:42.17,0:33:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胖胖的鯨井大叔了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:45.17,0:33:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:47.07,0:33:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在餐廳他跟蟹江先生借火柴的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:50.17,0:33:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神態就很不自然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:51.47,0:33:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外 最讓我在意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:55.07,0:33:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個大叔在上了甲板之後說的那句話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:57.77,0:33:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:00.57,0:34:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他...果然還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:06.17,0:34:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在看到那一萬元紙幣之後就嚇壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:10.47,0:34:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那張一萬元紙幣上寫的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:13.57,0:34:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海神波賽頓又賦予了我生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:15.77,0:34:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的影子也將再度復甦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:18.87,0:34:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的影子應該是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:20.27,0:34:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑影計畫師叶才三了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:23.77,0:34:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的復活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:24.57,0:34:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就表示他曾經死於他人之手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:28.37,0:34:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺他的人 恐怕就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:30.27,0:34:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起犯下那件案子的三個同夥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:33.77,0:34:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到 後來又出現了一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:36.17,0:34:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假冒早該命喪黃泉的叶才三的老人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:38.77,0:34:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我還是不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:41.47,0:34:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從那之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:42.27,0:34:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個從船上消失的老先生的真實身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:45.67,0:34:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有為什麼他們三個特地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:48.87,0:34:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要在法律追訴期過了的時候在船上見面？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:50.67,0:34:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至還去登什麼廣告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:53.27,0:34:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:54.17,0:34:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也懷疑那個登廣告自稱叫古川大的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:58.47,0:35:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們三個人之中誰用的才是本名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:01.37,0:35:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:02.47,0:35:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:03.57,0:35:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在的線索全都在那個大叔身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:06.37,0:35:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看他那副德性 隨便問問一定馬上就招了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:09.17,0:35:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:11.37,0:35:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 你說你不記得了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:13.57,0:35:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在甲板的時候 明明就是你自己說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:16.07,0:35:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就知道他還活著 這些話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:18.47,0:35:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...我真的有說這句話嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:20.87,0:35:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少跟我裝蒜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:22.67,0:35:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快 說出來你就輕鬆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:26.67,0:35:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你所說的 就是叶才三對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:30.77,0:35:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:32.77,0:35:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的什麼都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:35.47,0:35:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:37.67,0:35:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣根本沒完沒了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:40.27,0:35:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,組長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:42.17,0:35:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才去問過船上的船員了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:44.57,0:35:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:46.57,0:35:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每一位船員都有不在場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:49.57,0:35:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那起爆炸發生的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:52.17,0:35:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了船長和乘客之外的所有船員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:55.27,0:35:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是採取兩個人以上的方式行動的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:57.97,0:35:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:58.67,0:36:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們在這裡聽到類似槍聲的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:00.57,0:36:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕到上面的甲板查看了之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:02.87,0:36:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才發生那起爆炸的意外的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:05.27,0:36:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以被火燒成焦屍的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:06.77,0:36:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是當時不在甲板的人才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:09.57,0:36:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照你這些話的意思是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:11.87,0:36:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兇手只有可能是還沒有現身的叶才三了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:14.87,0:36:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該還有一個人吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:17.47,0:36:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:18.67,0:36:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個不舒服早早回房休息的龜田啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:22.47,0:36:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後我就再也沒有看到他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:25.77,0:36:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:27.27,0:36:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:28.17,0:36:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快到他房裡把他帶到這裡來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:30.67,0:36:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:32.57,0:36:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也陪大叔過去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:34.27,0:36:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:35.07,0:36:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 等等嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:37.87,0:36:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:44.47,0:36:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 我了解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:47.27,0:36:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 到了再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:49.17,0:36:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:51.67,0:36:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在就直接前往小笠原了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:53.77,0:36:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船長 你不打算折返嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:55.67,0:36:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:56.57,0:36:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天一早 他們就派直升機過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:58.77,0:36:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們船上現在搭載了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:59.67,0:37:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要送到島上去的生活物資
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:03.27,0:37:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切準備就緒之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:04.57,0:37:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總局也會派船出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:06.67,0:37:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這之前呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:07.37,0:37:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們只有把這件案子交給那位大偵探了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:10.87,0:37:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引擎啟動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:12.07,0:37:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,速度上升到20節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:14.07,0:37:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引擎啟動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:15.27,0:37:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引擎啟動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:19.87,0:37:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龜田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:22.37,0:37:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龜田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:24.47,0:37:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傷腦筋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:25.17,0:37:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看你們再去借把鑰匙來好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:28.57,0:37:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,門沒鎖啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:31.37,0:37:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龜田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:32.37,0:37:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:38.07,0:37:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人不在房裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:41.57,0:37:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:42.27,0:37:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們還是快點去通知鮫崎叔叔比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:45.17,0:37:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 服部平次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:49.87,0:37:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人呢 跑到哪裡去了啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:52.77,0:37:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,服部 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:34.47,0:38:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 有什麼發現沒有？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:40.87,0:38:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在下面的機房裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:42.57,0:38:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我發現地板沾了一點血跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:44.87,0:38:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有手槍的空彈殼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:46.67,0:38:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另外 就是這封奇怪的信了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:49.77,0:38:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也找到了這張不尋常的紙片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:52.37,0:38:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然已經被揉成一團當成垃圾丟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:54.77,0:38:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪裡找到的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:55.87,0:38:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,餐廳入口那裡不是有個洗手間嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:57.97,0:38:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在垃圾桶裡面找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:59.97,0:39:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洗手間的垃圾桶...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:02.07,0:39:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:03.47,0:39:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那封信上到底寫了些什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:06.27,0:39:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到機房去等我 古川大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:09.97,0:39:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼又是古川大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:12.27,0:39:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,血跡還有空的彈殼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:19.37,0:39:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 太陽穴被人射了一槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:22.57,0:39:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這的確是子彈的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:25.47,0:39:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個被燒焦的人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:27.67,0:39:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他先是看了這封信找到機房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:30.47,0:39:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡 被人用重物擊中頭部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:32.77,0:39:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才被放進這個箱子裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:34.27,0:39:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我想應該就是這個樣子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:39.17,0:39:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 你找到的那張紙上又寫了些什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:41.47,0:39:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想應該和那封信一樣都是用電腦打的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:46.97,0:39:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們到船尾見面 古川大上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:50.27,0:39:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可以證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:51.17,0:39:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人刻意要把鯨井先生引到甲板上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:54.97,0:39:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道這是寫給鯨井的呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:57.77,0:39:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為有兩個船員曾經親眼看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:00.57,0:40:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,12點一過鯨井就青著一張臉走到船尾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:02.97,0:40:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,扯開喉嚨大叫「喂 我來了」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:06.67,0:40:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後來那個船員張口跟他說話的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:08.67,0:40:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他還嚇了一大跳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:10.87,0:40:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們千萬不要跟別人提起我來過這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:13.97,0:40:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後來他才回到休息室加入我們的遊戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:19.17,0:40:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:19.97,0:40:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些船員想可能還會有誰到這裡來就一直在這裡等著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:23.57,0:40:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後誰也沒來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:25.27,0:40:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們正想回去工作的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:26.87,0:40:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就聽到上面的甲板那裡傳來了那聲槍響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:31.17,0:40:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:32.07,0:40:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個箱子起火了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:33.37,0:40:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 那個箱子還沒有起火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:35.47,0:40:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,箱子裡又找不到任何自動引爆的裝置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:39.27,0:40:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 兇手先在上面的甲板製造出槍聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:42.97,0:40:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接著又將旗子點著火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:44.87,0:40:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁著大家趕到上面的甲板去的空檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:46.87,0:40:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又走到這下面放火燒了這個急救箱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:51.17,0:40:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:52.17,0:40:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就難怪鯨井會嚇得魂都沒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:55.17,0:40:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 要是一個不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:57.57,0:41:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說不定就在這裡一起被人燒成焦屍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:01.57,0:41:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在的問題是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:03.57,0:41:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兇手在上面的甲板對天鳴槍之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:06.67,0:41:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有可能在不碰到任何人的情況之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:08.67,0:41:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走到這裡來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:10.77,0:41:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:11.67,0:41:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然有了兇手的線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:13.37,0:41:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要知道這個細節也是遲早的問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:16.77,0:41:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道事情的原委了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:19.27,0:41:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 你也知道了啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:22.37,0:41:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣 我們就來對比答案吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:30.37,0:41:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:31.47,0:41:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個自稱是叶才三的神秘老人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:34.67,0:41:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果照你所說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:36.87,0:41:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要能在出了船之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:39.07,0:41:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,折回的途中不碰到任何人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:41.37,0:41:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後神不知鬼不覺地出現在船裡面的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:44.87,0:41:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這必定是兇手設下的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:47.27,0:41:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FAKE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:48.07,0:41:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,故佈疑陣 障眼法 假像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:51.67,0:41:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在可能犯案的一共有兩個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:54.77,0:41:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:55.67,0:41:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡最值得注意的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:57.77,0:41:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呈現熱僵硬現象的屍體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:59.87,0:42:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手肘只彎到臉部前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:02.27,0:42:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是膝蓋卻完全地蜷曲起來這一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:05.17,0:42:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然屍體放進箱子的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:06.97,0:42:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兇手是把屍體儘量往下挪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:08.57,0:42:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再把兩隻手放在頭部兩側向上舉起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:11.77,0:42:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一可能這麼做的也只有一個人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:15.27,0:42:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之所以這樣故佈疑陣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:17.57,0:42:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實是想讓人以為他被人殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:19.27,0:42:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實現在還躲在船上的某個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:23.67,0:42:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡說什麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:25.57,0:42:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:26.77,0:42:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這隻手錶就是最好的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:28.37,0:42:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有搞錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:29.97,0:42:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是兇手的陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:34.77,0:42:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這倒有意思了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:36.57,0:42:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到我們的推理也有相左的一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:40.87,0:42:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:42.57,0:42:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這還是認識以來的第一次呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:48.47,0:42:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:50.17,0:42:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰的推理正確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:52.97,0:42:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就來一較高下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:54.87,0:42:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:56.07,0:42:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:56.97,0:42:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把那隻錶回復吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:59.77,0:43:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要我讓這隻焦黑的錶指針重新轉動不成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:03.27,0:43:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:04.47,0:43:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是要你把它放回原位罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:08.57,0:43:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:11.17,0:43:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:12.27,0:43:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說龜田不在自己的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:14.97,0:43:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 我也稍微找了一下子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:17.67,0:43:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不像話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:18.67,0:43:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼大的人怎麼可能說不見就不見呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:21.47,0:43:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓開 我自己去找他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:29.07,0:43:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那...我也去找找了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:31.77,0:43:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾位就暫時待在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:34.07,0:43:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:34.77,0:43:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是個偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:36.67,0:43:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而他不過是個卸任的刑警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:40.17,0:43:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你們根本沒有權力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:41.77,0:43:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我們幾個人拘禁在這裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:44.57,0:43:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:46.67,0:43:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:47.97,0:43:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要回自己的房間去休息了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:50.87,0:43:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 我也回房了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:52.47,0:43:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:53.37,0:43:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:54.37,0:43:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們現在擅自行動太危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:57.57,0:43:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用不著您費心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:59.97,0:44:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們自己的小命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:01.27,0:44:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們自己會看好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:03.57,0:44:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不對?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:13.47,0:44:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該有才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:15.77,0:44:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我的推理沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:18.47,0:44:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他現在一定躲在某個大家不會注意到的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:27.47,0:44:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:30.57,0:44:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,容易藏身的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:32.07,0:44:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 一定有吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:33.17,0:44:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好比說平常不能進去的地方啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:35.97,0:44:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是平常絕對看不到的地方之類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:38.97,0:44:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:39.97,0:44:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個殺人犯現在也在這艘船上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:42.17,0:44:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還亂跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:44.37,0:44:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:46.37,0:44:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,服部呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:48.77,0:44:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們沒有碰到啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:54.07,0:44:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不...不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:58.17,0:45:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道我跟工藤全部都推理錯了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:03.17,0:45:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:04.17,0:45:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前方30公里航路沒有任何阻礙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:07.27,0:45:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:07.97,0:45:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立刻加速 朝23點前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:10.07,0:45:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,航速30節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:11.27,0:45:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,速度上升至30節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:17.97,0:45:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來 會是誰呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:20.97,0:45:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰才是兇手呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:37.87,0:45:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 你有沒有聽到奇怪的水聲？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:41.57,0:45:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的水聲？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:44.67,0:45:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許是鰹魚跳出水面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:06.87,0:46:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的聽到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:08.67,0:46:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個奇怪的水聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:10.27,0:46:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定有什麼東西掉到水裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:12.77,0:46:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不跟你說了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:13.97,0:46:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一定是魚跳出水面的聲音嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:16.47,0:46:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽人家說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:17.57,0:46:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一帶的鰹魚跟飛魚的產量向來就很驚人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:22.87,0:46:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 你看到那個操著關西口音的哥哥沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:26.17,0:46:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關西口音啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:28.27,0:46:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說的這個年輕人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:29.37,0:46:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才來跟我借過手電筒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:31.47,0:46:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,借手電筒？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:33.47,0:46:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:34.87,0:46:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就很有可能到甲板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:36.67,0:46:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找尋足以用來破案的線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:40.17,0:46:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個水聲 難道是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:44.07,0:46:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:46.67,0:46:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:47.97,0:46:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:48.87,0:46:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢伙精明得很
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:50.27,0:46:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會出事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:54.07,0:46:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,服部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:58.17,0:46:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,服部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:59.77,0:47:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:01.77,0:47:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在就回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:06.87,0:47:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,服部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:15.27,0:47:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:16.47,0:47:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:17.67,0:47:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,服部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:20.57,0:47:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,服部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:31.57,0:47:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,服部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:33.17,0:47:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:35.07,0:47:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣太危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:37.27,0:47:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是掉下去怎麼辦啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:38.87,0:47:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:39.47,0:47:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:42.77,0:47:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是誰掉進這麼一片汪洋大海裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:46.87,0:47:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都只是滄海中的一粟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:52.47,0:47:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都沒救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:54.77,0:47:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:57.77,0:47:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼到這裡來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:00.17,0:48:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 平次哥哥他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:03.27,0:48:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個臭小子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:05.37,0:48:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在一定又跑到什麼地方去找兇手的線索了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:08.87,0:48:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 你就別擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:11.27,0:48:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好 過一下他就會冒出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:16.37,0:48:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美...美海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:21.37,0:48:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不...不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:22.87,0:48:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的聲音...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:24.17,0:48:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很像我一個朋友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:27.67,0:48:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:28.57,0:48:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:30.07,0:48:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們三個怎麼都出現在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:32.77,0:48:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實是她拜託我們來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:34.47,0:48:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫她找個東西的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:36.97,0:48:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找個東西?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:38.37,0:48:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在找一個墜子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:40.67,0:48:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上床之前才發現它不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:42.67,0:48:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到處找都找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:44.07,0:48:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛好就碰到了他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:46.07,0:48:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看他們沒什麼事就請他們一起幫忙找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:48.87,0:48:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三個人 總比一個人要有效率多了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:52.67,0:48:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:54.27,0:48:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這個可以放相片的項鏈墜嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:58.17,0:48:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它的鎖鏈鬆掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:59.67,0:49:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是在船頭的附近發現它的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:03.97,0:49:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是它 謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:06.17,0:49:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想一定是我在傍晚的時候掉在那裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:09.87,0:49:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那照片上的女孩就是磯貝小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:13.27,0:49:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱著你的人就是你父親囉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:16.87,0:49:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:17.97,0:49:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼搞的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:18.87,0:49:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撿到了東西怎麼不立刻還給人家呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:21.17,0:49:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:22.87,0:49:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她父親的臉上被挖掉了一個大洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:25.37,0:49:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我根本就看不出來他長什麼樣子嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:27.87,0:49:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這張照片很有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:28.87,0:49:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是其他哪位先生跟自己的女兒照的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:33.17,0:49:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本來想晚餐的時候問問這是誰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:35.37,0:49:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是忘記了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:37.77,0:49:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:38.97,0:49:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才說挖了一個洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:40.47,0:49:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:41.67,0:49:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正這已經是20多年前的照片了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:45.27,0:49:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我父親留給我的遺物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:48.07,0:49:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就只剩下這個了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:52.97,0:49:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們到底還要不要命啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:55.27,0:49:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺人犯現在就在這艘船上你們還到處亂晃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:59.17,0:50:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:00.07,0:50:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會讓他們離開餐廳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:02.67,0:50:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是 是因為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:04.27,0:50:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們幾個說要回自己的房間休息嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:07.07,0:50:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:07.97,0:50:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們沒有那個權力命令我們做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:11.37,0:50:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我更不想跟一個歇斯底里的大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:14.27,0:50:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整天搞在一起沒完沒了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:16.87,0:50:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:18.77,0:50:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果說一個人太危險的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:19.87,0:50:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我寧可把房間上鎖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:21.77,0:50:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟這些小孩玩撲克牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:23.57,0:50:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩到天亮也比跟你們在一起要舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:27.77,0:50:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:28.87,0:50:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想 這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:30.77,0:50:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們這樣七零八落的好像還是不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:34.77,0:50:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是大家待在一個地方安全比較有保障啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:38.87,0:50:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:39.97,0:50:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是去找龜田先生了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:41.77,0:50:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了沒有啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:44.17,0:50:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:44.87,0:50:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他跟叶才三一樣不知道跑哪兒去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:48.77,0:50:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有看到服部？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:50.67,0:50:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:51.57,0:50:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連那個小夥子也不見了啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:55.57,0:50:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 這艘船到底怎麼回事啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:58.77,0:50:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:59.87,0:51:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從現在開始禁止任何人採取行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:03.17,0:51:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兇手一定是我們之外的某個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:05.87,0:51:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定兇手現在就在暗處伺機而動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:09.67,0:51:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等待我們其中的某個人落單的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:12.97,0:51:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔說得沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:15.07,0:51:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一開始聽到槍響的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:16.57,0:51:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鮫崎叔叔跟我們都待在休息室裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:19.47,0:51:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鮫崎先生上洗手間也回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:22.07,0:51:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:22.97,0:51:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在大家急忙跑進甲板查看情況的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:25.57,0:51:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船尾發生爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:27.17,0:51:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個裝有屍體的箱子也應聲起火了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:30.17,0:51:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們跑到上面的甲板之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:31.87,0:51:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有一個人中途脫離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:33.57,0:51:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就連中途才來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:34.77,0:51:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我們一起登上甲板的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:36.47,0:51:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海老名先生和磯貝小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:37.87,0:51:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不可能點火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:40.27,0:51:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:41.67,0:51:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就現階段那具被燒焦的焦屍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:44.17,0:51:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法辨認身份的情況來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:45.67,0:51:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一有可能點火引爆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:47.77,0:51:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是當時不在甲板上的龜田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:51.17,0:51:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蟹江先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:53.67,0:51:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再來就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:54.97,0:51:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個自稱為叶才三的這三個人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:59.27,0:52:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過問題到底是出在哪裡呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:02.07,0:52:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不但現在坐在這兒的人舉止怪異
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:05.87,0:52:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就連鮫崎對於這整件事情的發展
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:09.67,0:52:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也表現得太過於激烈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:12.87,0:52:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情一定不簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:15.27,0:52:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20年前那件案子一定還有內幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:27.87,0:52:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去一下洗手間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:30.07,0:52:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上回來哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:32.47,0:52:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 要是服部在的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:34.47,0:52:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就可以順理成章地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:35.87,0:52:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓叔叔他們瞭解始末了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:38.17,0:52:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他到底到哪裡去了啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:41.17,0:52:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(阿笠博士家)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:45.27,0:52:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:46.27,0:52:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怎麼啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:47.37,0:52:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 20年前的四億元搶案啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:50.47,0:52:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在正在看這件案子的特別報導呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:54.87,0:52:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼民法追訴期已經過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:56.87,0:52:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上就大肆報導了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:59.17,0:53:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我已經把它給錄下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:00.97,0:53:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想說過幾天給你看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:02.87,0:53:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電視上有提到關於歹徒的事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:05.27,0:53:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你等一下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:06.67,0:53:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才好像聽到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:10.97,0:53:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在是知道那個主謀叶才三的長相了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:13.97,0:53:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過其他三個同夥只登了模擬照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:16.57,0:53:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不知道他們的真實身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:19.67,0:53:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有提到叶才三死了的事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:22.57,0:53:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:23.27,0:53:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,報導說當年有一件上面有彈痕和血跡的上衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:25.67,0:53:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漂到岸邊被撈起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:27.07,0:53:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以警方認定他一定是被同夥黑吃黑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:30.57,0:53:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後才會遇害身亡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:32.37,0:53:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 他們怎麼會知道那是叶才三的衣服呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:35.87,0:53:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為警方在那件上衣口袋裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:38.87,0:53:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到一張據說他向來貼身帶在身邊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:41.77,0:53:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱著他女兒的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:45.77,0:53:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有這種事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:47.27,0:53:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說來這件事還真是夠淒慘的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:49.77,0:53:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據說當年一個犯人受了防盜警鈴的驚嚇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:52.27,0:53:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就開始拿槍亂射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:53.97,0:53:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不長眼睛的子彈正巧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:55.67,0:53:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就把當時在銀行上班的鮫崎小姐給射死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:59.87,0:54:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說子彈射到誰了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:01.37,0:54:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個女性銀行職員啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:03.47,0:54:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的名字叫做鮫崎美海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:05.77,0:54:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可憐喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:07.27,0:54:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年紀輕輕就死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:08.97,0:54:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鮫崎美海...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:11.37,0:54:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:12.57,0:54:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一切未免太過巧合了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:15.97,0:54:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼跟當年那起案子相關的各方人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:19.07,0:54:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在全集中到這艘船上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:21.77,0:54:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,策劃這次旅遊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:23.97,0:54:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個古川大又是什麼人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:27.27,0:54:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在這件事裡面到底扮演了什麼角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:36.17,0:54:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才是什麼聲音啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:38.07,0:54:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要先掛電話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:39.57,0:54:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要是發現什麼情報的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:41.07,0:54:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再打電話給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:44.67,0:54:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聲音從哪兒傳來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:46.17,0:54:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽是從船尾傳來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:48.17,0:54:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 我從左邊繞過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:49.97,0:54:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你從右邊過去 記住動作一定要快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:51.77,0:54:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:54.67,0:54:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:14.17,0:55:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:16.47,0:55:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能呢 再找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:18.87,0:55:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:21.07,0:55:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了 服部？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:24.47,0:55:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼還不出來？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:26.57,0:55:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照你平常的個性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:28.07,0:55:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽到聲音早就跑出來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:31.27,0:55:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是出了什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:33.77,0:55:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,服部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:35.97,0:55:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,組長啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:37.27,0:55:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定那個傢伙利用這個地方還待在船上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:40.87,0:55:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叶才三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:44.57,0:55:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兇手一定就是叶才三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:46.77,0:55:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他這樣到處亂開槍為的就是要擾亂我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:51.07,0:55:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 他這樣做是為了什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:53.37,0:55:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是為了我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:57.17,0:56:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一定是想把我給殺掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:01.77,0:56:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:03.57,0:56:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...我還不想死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:06.07,0:56:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還不想就這麼死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:10.17,0:56:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我求求你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:12.07,0:56:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要你肯保住我這條命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:13.97,0:56:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想知道什麼我都告訴你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:21.77,0:56:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:24.57,0:56:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是在20年前和叶才三一起犯下強盜殺人案的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:28.27,0:56:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那三個同夥之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:31.87,0:56:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以坐上這艘船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:33.67,0:56:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為的只是想和從前的三個兄弟一起分享
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:37.17,0:56:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20年後脫罪的喜悅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:39.37,0:56:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們一個兄弟寄了一封信給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:41.97,0:56:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說只要船一離岸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:43.67,0:56:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在法律追訴期之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:44.77,0:56:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們永遠不可能被抓回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:47.57,0:56:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他還在信裡塞了一萬元錢的舊幣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:51.37,0:56:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我們這麼多年都沒見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:54.67,0:56:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家又換了不同的名字和容貌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:57.17,0:56:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一開始我根本就認不出誰是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:59.87,0:57:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直到蟹江他先開口跟我說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:03.37,0:57:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才從他那裡得知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:05.17,0:57:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們當年另一個兄弟就是龜田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:07.97,0:57:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:08.77,0:57:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說的那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:09.97,0:57:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直想要你小命的傢伙是誰啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:13.77,0:57:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:16.57,0:57:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:18.87,0:57:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你少裝蒜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:20.37,0:57:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看就是被你們窩裡反的叶才三對吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:23.77,0:57:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不可能有這種事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:25.57,0:57:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早在20年前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:26.87,0:57:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就被我們一個兄弟用槍給射死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:29.47,0:57:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那會不會是你們哪個兄弟呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:32.67,0:57:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來他就能獨吞那些錢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:35.27,0:57:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你們那些錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:36.87,0:57:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該都還沒有用吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:38.67,0:57:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一開始的時候也是這麼想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:41.57,0:57:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是這樣也不對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:43.87,0:57:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情根本就說不通嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:47.67,0:57:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:49.57,0:57:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心 快趴下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:52.07,0:57:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還好吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:53.17,0:57:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 哪裡受傷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:58.37,0:57:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要亂動啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:03.47,0:58:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,槍傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:06.07,0:58:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 到底是從哪射來的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:12.17,0:58:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼頭 快趴下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:14.97,0:58:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外面有個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:16.67,0:58:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:17.77,0:58:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在船頭那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:19.57,0:58:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 這次看你往哪裡跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:22.07,0:58:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鮫崎組長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:29.37,0:58:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在已經無處可逃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:32.77,0:58:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立刻把槍放下 乖乖束手就縛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:36.87,0:58:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叶才三 你聽到了沒有?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:39.17,0:58:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是叶才三對不對?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:44.77,0:58:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是說句話啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:48.27,0:58:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是 蟹江
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:52.37,0:58:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:04.27,0:59:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太陽穴中了一槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:06.67,0:59:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當場死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:09.37,0:59:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的身體倒還挺暖的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:11.37,0:59:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,血液也還沒有凝固
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:13.87,0:59:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太陽穴上也有抵著槍口開槍會留下的焦痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:19.37,0:59:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了蟹江之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:21.37,0:59:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們所有人都還待在餐廳裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:26.37,0:59:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來就只能解釋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:27.67,0:59:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蟹江是自己拿著手槍朝腦袋射擊的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:32.07,0:59:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:33.47,0:59:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蟹江剛才就一直躲在船頭這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:36.47,0:59:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看著自己當年的兄弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:37.47,0:59:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在餐廳裡滔滔不絕地敍述20年前的往事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:40.37,0:59:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後實在聽不下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:42.67,0:59:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才忍不住開槍加以殺害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:45.27,0:59:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本不想留活口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:47.17,0:59:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他明知自己沒有退路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:49.37,0:59:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後才會舉槍自盡吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:53.67,0:59:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是蠢蛋一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:55.27,0:59:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 你不覺得奇怪嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:59.37,1:00:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前在船尾被燒焦的焦屍
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:01.57,1:00:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身上明明穿著蟹江的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:03.37,1:00:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴著他的手錶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:04.67,1:00:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼...那具焦屍到底又是誰呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:08.67,1:00:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想那恐怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:09.87,1:00:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是他在這艘船上
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:11.67,1:00:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失蹤的另一個兄弟 龜田
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:13.97,1:00:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然就是叶才三了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:17.27,1:00:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過不管是哪一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:18.77,1:00:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兇手絕對是蟹江
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:21.07,1:00:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他讓屍體弄成自己的裝扮
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:22.97,1:00:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放火燒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:24.17,1:00:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為的就是讓大家都以為他已經被燒死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:27.07,1:00:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問題是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:28.17,1:00:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蟹江在這段時間到底是怎麼躲過我們的搜查
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:31.37,1:00:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後跑到這邊來埋伏的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:34.47,1:00:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:36.57,1:00:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個叔叔的後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:38.07,1:00:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還綁了一個奇怪的東西耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:41.07,1:00:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是繩索梯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:46.77,1:00:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果在這裡玩捉迷藏
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:48.27,1:00:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定不會被發現哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:49.97,1:00:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:51.27,1:00:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蟹江就是抓住了這條繩索才會躲過我們所有的搜查
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:55.67,1:00:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的手掌上的確有
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:57.27,1:00:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幾處繩子摩擦的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:59.77,1:01:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從這個角度看應該沒有錯才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:01.77,1:01:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我搞不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:04.07,1:01:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他刻意讓我們以為他死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:07.07,1:01:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後又躲在這個地方到底是為了什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:09.67,1:01:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只能夠想到
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:11.67,1:01:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是想突然出現在下一個殺害對象的面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:14.47,1:01:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為的就是讓他在死前感覺到恐懼罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:20.17,1:01:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你說 有哪個人會做這種事最後又把蟹江給殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:23.97,1:01:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛才中了槍傷的鯨井不也是他過去的兄弟嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:29.67,1:01:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這倒是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:38.57,1:01:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 流了這麼多血
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:40.47,1:01:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看 一定是動脈被打到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:43.97,1:01:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得儘快幫你包紮才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:46.27,1:01:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭已經去找服務員要急救箱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:50.67,1:01:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 你這條狗命還真幸運啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:54.97,1:01:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只不過在西裝還有手臂上
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:57.47,1:01:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多了個洞就沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:58.97,1:02:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛利 我找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:01.27,1:02:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是子彈射穿的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:03.37,1:02:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來子彈是從蟹江所在的船頭穿過玻璃
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:07.47,1:02:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射進餐廳裡面的沒錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:09.57,1:02:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 只要能夠找到那顆子彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:13.17,1:02:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不難了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:14.67,1:02:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問 是不是這個東西啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:20.97,1:02:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就是那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:23.37,1:02:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙還真有本事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:25.97,1:02:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有打中目標的要害
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:28.07,1:02:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能讓子彈一下子飛這麼遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:31.47,1:02:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道你忘記了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:32.67,1:02:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當年跟叶才三犯案的同夥
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:35.37,1:02:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當中有一個人對於使用武器本來就相當熟練
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:38.87,1:02:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:39.87,1:02:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說那個傢伙曾經參加哪一國的外國軍團
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:44.57,1:02:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,技術非常了得
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:46.77,1:02:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 可見這個傢伙就是蟹江了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:51.87,1:02:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:53.47,1:02:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳把急救箱拿來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:57.97,1:02:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:59.67,1:03:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也只有先幫他止止血了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:03.27,1:03:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:06.47,1:03:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該在這附近吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:09.77,1:03:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 操關西口音的年輕人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:12.77,1:03:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從他來這裡借了手電筒以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:14.87,1:03:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就沒有再到控制室來過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:17.17,1:03:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:18.47,1:03:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他會到哪裡去呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:20.87,1:03:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:21.57,1:03:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可不可以請你到大家的房間去找一找啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:24.57,1:03:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是可以啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:25.57,1:03:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過他應該不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:26.97,1:03:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:27.87,1:03:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我們跟鮫崎先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:30.07,1:03:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起去找一個叫龜田先生的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:31.97,1:03:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就已經把其他的房間全部都已經找過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:34.77,1:03:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:35.37,1:03:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有哪個房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:36.57,1:03:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有被人翻動過的痕跡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:38.57,1:03:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為那個哥哥是個偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:42.07,1:03:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這倒是沒有發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:43.97,1:03:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為除了龜田先生的房間之外全部都上了鎖
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:47.07,1:03:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:48.27,1:03:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們倒是沒有去找那個房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:51.07,1:03:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過那個房間非常的整齊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:54.07,1:03:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:54.77,1:03:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個戴副眼鏡
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:56.07,1:03:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海老名先生的房間啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:57.37,1:04:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他除了房間裡面放了一個皮箱
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:00.27,1:04:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,床上連折痕都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:02.37,1:04:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子就知道還沒有把皮箱打開過
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:05.37,1:04:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:07.27,1:04:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:07.97,1:04:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能帶我到那個房間去看一看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:10.37,1:04:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是毛利叔叔拜託我這麼做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:17.77,1:04:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:20.77,1:04:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:27.37,1:04:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:28.57,1:04:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛利偵探真的有交待你要做這種事情嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:32.17,1:04:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另外
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:33.17,1:04:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他還要你對大家保守這個秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:35.97,1:04:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們快點到船艙裡面去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:37.87,1:04:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個屍體 看得我發毛
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:39.87,1:04:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:41.87,1:04:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:42.47,1:04:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也要快點回到大家那裡去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:44.67,1:04:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:46.37,1:04:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到這次旅行會變成這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:49.07,1:04:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說兇手已經舉槍自盡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:51.47,1:04:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,策劃這次旅行的古川先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:53.77,1:04:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定還在小笠原那裡高興地等這艘船到岸呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:59.47,1:05:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古川大
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:02.17,1:05:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這趟旅行的策劃人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:04.57,1:05:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切的謎團都是由此而起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:07.37,1:05:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果 兇手就是蟹江
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:10.27,1:05:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而這個古川大的真正身份就是蟹江的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:13.57,1:05:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大部分的事情就連得起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:16.87,1:05:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我總覺得怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:19.37,1:05:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了那個焦屍上戴著的金錶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:22.87,1:05:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有龜田先生拿著的那個刻有古川字樣的印章
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:26.87,1:05:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都叫我覺得納悶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:28.97,1:05:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:29.97,1:05:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少能弄清楚這個古川大是誰的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:42.97,1:05:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生 請問一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:45.37,1:05:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們有沒有看到一個戴著眼鏡的小男孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:49.07,1:05:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:51.27,1:05:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個古川大是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:59.17,1:06:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,燒焦的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:01.97,1:06:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另一邊還有
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:03.37,1:06:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剝落的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:05.97,1:06:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:10.87,1:06:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:25.97,1:06:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:36.27,1:06:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:38.37,1:06:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:39.67,1:06:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能夠控制時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:41.17,1:06:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有大家的行動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:43.27,1:06:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難怪他要找服部這個偵探來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:46.47,1:06:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過幹嘛非找服部不可呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:49.47,1:06:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在關西地區也許的確是小有名氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:52.77,1:06:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不必刻意找大阪的偵探啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:00.77,1:07:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼這麼愛到處亂跑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:02.77,1:07:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次都讓人家為你擔心受怕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:05.77,1:07:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正要回去了 所以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:10.07,1:07:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算我拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:14.37,1:07:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要丟下我一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:32.97,1:07:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:34.27,1:07:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明明知道我膽子很小的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:37.37,1:07:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只要一不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:39.07,1:07:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就必須一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:40.47,1:07:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這艘陰森的船上到處找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:43.77,1:07:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:45.87,1:07:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 這個網球是哪來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:49.97,1:07:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我剛才在餐廳裡找你的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:52.57,1:07:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一張桌子底下撿到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:55.17,1:07:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也問過大家是誰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:56.67,1:07:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都說不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:58.77,1:08:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個鮫崎叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:00.07,1:08:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到這顆球怎麼說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:03.37,1:08:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒拿給他看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:04.27,1:08:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就跟爸爸一起往船頭的方向去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:07.47,1:08:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們還同時叫了好大一聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:09.97,1:08:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說是什麼他們在蟹江先生的身體上
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:12.17,1:08:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了一個非常舊的傷口
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:16.17,1:08:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 毛利叔叔他們一開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:19.37,1:08:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了找那個叫叶才三的人從餐廳離開的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:22.17,1:08:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他人都在哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:23.57,1:08:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在不同的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:26.87,1:08:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:27.87,1:08:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸跟服部回到餐廳的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:29.67,1:08:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們也全都回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:32.67,1:08:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:34.47,1:08:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我全都看穿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:37.27,1:08:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件案子的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:50.27,1:08:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一切原委我都清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:53.07,1:08:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在就剩下證據的搜索
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:55.77,1:08:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:56.97,1:08:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有看到一位操關西口音的男孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:00.17,1:09:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才一個小男孩來問過之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:02.27,1:09:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也在到處找他
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:06.07,1:09:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:07.27,1:09:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在我不方便說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:08.97,1:09:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待會兒 我再打電話給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:12.37,1:09:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:13.27,1:09:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:14.17,1:09:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就叫所有人再去找一次好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:16.47,1:09:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就麻煩你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:21.27,1:09:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你在這裡做什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:24.47,1:09:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:25.87,1:09:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他到底會到哪裡去了呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:28.27,1:09:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:29.67,1:09:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還會有誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:30.97,1:09:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說的當然是服部啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:33.97,1:09:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是說平次哥哥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:36.37,1:09:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想他現在一定快樂地跟魚在一起游泳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:42.67,1:09:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛利 你說這該不會是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:48.67,1:09:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:53.87,1:09:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:58.57,1:09:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:00.07,1:10:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼啦 叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:03.27,1:10:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:04.47,1:10:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:05.67,1:10:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:06.57,1:10:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你立刻叫所有的乘客到這兒來集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:10.27,1:10:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經把案子都解開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:13.27,1:10:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:14.77,1:10:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:20.67,1:10:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是真的把案子解開了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:23.87,1:10:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:25.07,1:10:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於這整件案子的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:27.77,1:10:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都已經解開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:30.57,1:10:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會說
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:31.27,1:10:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個蟹江不是兇手吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:33.77,1:10:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 兇手的確是蟹江沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:37.47,1:10:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它也的確如組長所說
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:39.27,1:10:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一開始裝死之後潛伏在船上
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:42.07,1:10:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為的就是等待下手殺人的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:44.97,1:10:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他想殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:46.17,1:10:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是鯨井先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:48.17,1:10:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 你說的那個被燒死的人又是誰呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:51.37,1:10:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個是龜田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:53.57,1:10:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一開始的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:55.57,1:10:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蟹江 先把龜田先生找了出來射殺之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:59.47,1:11:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再把他放進
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:01.37,1:11:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,位於船尾用來放緊急救生梯的箱子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:03.07,1:11:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後 就回到大家身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:06.67,1:11:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後來 又點火將甲板上的旗子點燃
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:09.77,1:11:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我們全跑到甲板查看的時候把箱子燒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:14.27,1:11:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在把龜田先生放進箱子的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:16.67,1:11:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之所以沒有立刻為他穿上衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:19.07,1:11:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為的就是想
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:20.27,1:11:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等待鮫崎組長放棄找尋那個神秘老人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:24.77,1:11:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果幫他穿上衣服會花不少時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:27.67,1:11:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來也有被組長發現的顧慮
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:30.87,1:11:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那具焦屍的手臂會放在臉頰兩邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:33.77,1:11:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是最好的證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:36.57,1:11:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放屍體的時候如果能將兩手向上伸直
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:39.27,1:11:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屍體就算是死後僵硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:42.07,1:11:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿起衣服來也會方便很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:44.37,1:11:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至於他的錶帶之所以鬆脫
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:47.17,1:11:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為蟹江的手錶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:48.67,1:11:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法完全吻合龜田先生的手腕的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:51.67,1:11:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,點火之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:53.77,1:11:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蟹江又將鯨井先生約到了船尾見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:56.97,1:11:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果順利 就可以誣陷他是兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:00.27,1:12:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟在案發之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:01.67,1:12:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就出現在命案現場的人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:03.37,1:12:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總是會第一個遭到眾人懷疑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:05.77,1:12:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那他為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:07.07,1:12:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非要故意讓大家以為他已經死掉了呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:11.27,1:12:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了出現在下一個目標鯨井先生面前的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:15.27,1:12:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能讓他在第一時間感覺到恐懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:18.57,1:12:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他畢竟是20年前
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:20.07,1:12:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,背叛了自己的兄弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:22.57,1:12:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,背叛了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:24.07,1:12:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 那個化名叶才三的老人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:27.17,1:12:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是兇手為了嚇人創造出來根本不具實體的分身
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:31.57,1:12:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們可以看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:32.97,1:12:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蟹江胸口上的那幾個傷痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:36.97,1:12:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些受到槍擊留下的傷口就是最有力的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:41.57,1:12:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難不成
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:43.87,1:12:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:45.37,1:12:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是大家都以為20年前
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:47.57,1:12:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就葬身海底的黑影計畫師
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:51.77,1:12:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是叶才三本人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:56.57,1:12:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不...不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:00.87,1:13:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:05.67,1:13:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:06.87,1:13:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個男人絕不可能是叶才三
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:10.57,1:13:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為 叶才三
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:16.17,1:13:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是我的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:20.77,1:13:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是妳父親?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:23.37,1:13:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:24.87,1:13:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑影計畫師叶才三
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:27.97,1:13:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是我的親生父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:30.77,1:13:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以參加這個旅行團
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:32.97,1:13:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為的就是要尋找我那傳說在20年前
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:36.47,1:13:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遭到同伴殺害的父親的下落
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:39.57,1:13:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我總是想
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:40.97,1:13:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他現在也許還在人世
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:43.87,1:13:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後才確定他已經死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:47.17,1:13:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說不定去整形改變了容貌
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:50.87,1:13:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把我當成什麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:52.47,1:13:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算他改變了容貌
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:54.67,1:13:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這個女兒會認不出來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:57.07,1:13:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信我父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:58.57,1:13:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果看到我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:59.77,1:14:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定也會有不同的反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:02.47,1:14:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:03.87,1:14:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經有20年沒有見面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:06.77,1:14:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想聽的就是這番證詞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:10.47,1:14:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 磯貝小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:12.57,1:14:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我原先也只是假設
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:14.57,1:14:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直沒有辦法找到實證
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:16.67,1:14:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來 就無法完全摧毀兇手的計畫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:20.97,1:14:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,計畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:22.67,1:14:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:23.87,1:14:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兇手先讓我們大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:26.37,1:14:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以為蟹江射殺龜田以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:27.97,1:14:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再將他打扮成自己的樣子放火焚屍
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:30.67,1:14:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓大家產生他已經死亡的錯覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:33.47,1:14:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後 又藏匿行蹤到處亂開槍 攪亂我們的思緒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:37.27,1:14:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後來又在船頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:38.97,1:14:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊自己過去的兄弟鯨井先生之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:42.67,1:14:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自認沒有退路 最後只有舉槍自盡
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:45.27,1:14:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實這些全是他的障眼法
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:48.57,1:14:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為的是讓我們以為
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:51.07,1:14:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蟹江就是叶才三
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:52.67,1:14:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而這一幕幕殺人罪行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:54.87,1:14:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是他為20年前兄弟的背叛
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:56.97,1:14:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,演出的復仇記
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:59.97,1:15:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 這麼說 兇手是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:03.67,1:15:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:05.17,1:15:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兇手另有其人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:07.27,1:15:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且就在這裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:11.97,1:15:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託 毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:13.17,1:15:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有搞錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:15.97,1:15:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你應該都很清楚才對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:18.17,1:15:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在船尾發生爆炸的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:20.77,1:15:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在在場的人全都到了上面的甲板
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:25.07,1:15:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他的船員也都有不在場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:27.97,1:15:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是也說過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:29.57,1:15:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有自動引爆裝置的話是無法...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:32.77,1:15:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兇手的確是用了自動引爆裝置
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:36.57,1:15:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是放在箱子裡面嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:38.57,1:15:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實就是香煙
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:40.37,1:15:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他先把汽油罐放在箱子裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:42.97,1:15:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再把點燃的香煙放在箱邊的開口上
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:45.07,1:15:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉上一條細線穩住
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:47.47,1:15:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等到十分鐘以後 線被燒斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:51.87,1:15:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,煙蒂就自會掉進箱子裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:53.57,1:15:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來 火苗就會自動竄起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:59.97,1:16:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 船尾那四發
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:02.17,1:16:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有船頭那兩發類似槍響的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:05.37,1:16:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你又怎麼解釋
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:06.97,1:16:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時在場的人也是一樣全部都在...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:09.87,1:16:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也是香煙搞的鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:12.17,1:16:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,依我推斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:13.07,1:16:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兇手是把鞭炮黏在香煙上
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:15.27,1:16:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再把香煙利用膠帶輕輕貼在欄杆上
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:18.87,1:16:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鞭炮一旦爆炸 所有的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:21.17,1:16:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自會掉進海裡面 消失得無影無蹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:24.07,1:16:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欄杆上燒黑的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:26.67,1:16:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和油漆剝落就是最好的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:30.57,1:16:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,順便一提
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:31.57,1:16:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這甲板上傳出爆炸聲 旗子就起火燃燒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:34.67,1:16:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是兇手把旗子沾滿汽油之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:36.87,1:16:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又同樣的在旗子上粘上了爆竹製造的效果
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:41.67,1:16:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以只要利用香煙輔助
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:44.67,1:16:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是誰 都有可能犯下這場殺人罪行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:50.97,1:16:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:52.67,1:16:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兇手到底是什麼人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:55.27,1:16:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經來不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:10.17,1:17:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後方發生爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:12.37,1:17:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引擎停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:13.57,1:17:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立刻調查各部位的損傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:14.97,1:17:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:22.17,1:17:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下面 有沒有哪裡受損？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:24.77,1:17:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:26.67,1:17:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們大可不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:29.07,1:17:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次炸彈爆炸的位置在後方100公尺
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:31.47,1:17:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不至於有危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:34.17,1:17:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炸彈在後方100公尺？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:36.27,1:17:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那真的是炸彈嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:38.97,1:17:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為求慎重
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:40.77,1:17:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我事先用繩子拉住了橡皮艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:43.27,1:17:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將繩子綁在船尾的欄杆上
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:45.47,1:17:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再讓橡皮艇跟在船身後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:47.87,1:17:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海老名先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:49.67,1:17:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是你那裝了定時炸彈的皮箱
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:53.57,1:17:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,皮箱？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:56.37,1:17:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼知道的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:59.87,1:18:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你房間的床上整齊得連皺紋都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:03.77,1:18:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,皮箱又沒有開過的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:06.17,1:18:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再加上你不時注意時間的那副模樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:09.07,1:18:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我心裡就已經有數了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:10.87,1:18:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那顆炸彈恐怕是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:12.77,1:18:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了將20年前犯下那件搶案的歹徒全部除掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:16.87,1:18:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在很早以前就準備好了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:19.47,1:18:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為的是對當年殺害你同事的殺人犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:23.37,1:18:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進行報復對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:26.67,1:18:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:27.67,1:18:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他數鈔票的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:29.37,1:18:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種不同於常人的數法
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:31.47,1:18:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有銀行的職員才會那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:33.87,1:18:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他還一度喃喃自語地說
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:37.77,1:18:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那位在搶案中遇害女職員的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:40.17,1:18:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是鮫崎美海的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:44.27,1:18:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不只是普通同事的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:46.97,1:18:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她還是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:48.87,1:18:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在世上最重要最重要的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:53.67,1:18:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道你就是那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:54.77,1:18:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我女兒喪禮上大哭的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:57.47,1:18:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:59.67,1:19:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從那天起我就離開銀行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:02.37,1:19:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不斷地更換工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:04.27,1:19:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用我自己的方式追蹤兇手的下落
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:07.27,1:19:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算追訴期過了也要繼續下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:11.37,1:19:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 原來美海當年
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:14.37,1:19:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說要讓我見的重要人物就是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:20.27,1:19:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是你 要是你在那天
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:24.47,1:19:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能依照約定的時間來到銀行的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:28.07,1:19:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她也不會碰上那種事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:34.07,1:19:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:37.17,1:19:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天我一個手下遇刺
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:39.97,1:19:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道出事的時候我人正在醫院
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:46.37,1:19:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:47.67,1:19:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到那則廣告才來參加這個旅行團的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:51.87,1:19:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 其實我也不太確定
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:55.27,1:19:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心想要是不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:56.97,1:20:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就在爆炸之前把皮箱丟到海裡去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:04.97,1:20:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:06.77,1:20:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次將當年的兇手一個個殺害的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:12.17,1:20:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:13.47,1:20:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是我幹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:15.07,1:20:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只不過把炸彈帶上船而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:17.47,1:20:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有帶什麼手槍啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:19.47,1:20:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:20.57,1:20:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們要相信我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:21.97,1:20:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:24.27,1:20:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你並不是兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:27.57,1:20:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才也已經說過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:29.77,1:20:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過兇手讓蟹江背起兇手的黑鍋
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:32.67,1:20:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藉以完成這一起20年後的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:34.17,1:20:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,復仇大戰的角度來看的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:37.97,1:20:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件案子根本說不通
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:40.67,1:20:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兇手先偽裝成老人登上船之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:43.17,1:20:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁著藉口外出的時候解除偽裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:45.57,1:20:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再度登上船來製造叶才三現身的假像
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:49.77,1:20:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另外呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:51.27,1:20:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又在甲板上留下寫有叶才三署名的鈔票
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:54.67,1:20:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一切都是為了對背叛他的兄弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:57.27,1:21:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進行一場恐怖的心理威嚇
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:01.37,1:21:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 即使如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:02.67,1:21:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果蟹江身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:04.47,1:21:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那些槍擊留下的疤痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:06.67,1:21:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兇手就絕對沒有辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:08.47,1:21:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,順利地讓大家誤以為
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:10.27,1:21:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是他在20年前被同伴射殺的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:13.37,1:21:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 那傷是怎麼來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:15.57,1:21:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想那些傷疤
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:16.87,1:21:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是他過去在外國傭兵部隊留下的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:20.67,1:21:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們之中不是有一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:22.67,1:21:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擁有這種特殊經歷嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:24.67,1:21:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是說 他是當年的歹徒之中...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:29.27,1:21:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:30.37,1:21:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:31.27,1:21:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從這個角度來思考的話兇手只有可能是一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:34.97,1:21:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早就知道蟹江身上有那些舊傷疤的人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:39.17,1:21:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:40.27,1:21:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過去和他曾經是兄弟的鯨井先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:43.17,1:21:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就只有你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:47.27,1:21:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:50.47,1:21:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你先是在餐廳裡面看到龜田先生離席以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:54.77,1:21:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁著大家聽到叶才三的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:56.67,1:21:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騷動之際先到了機房
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:59.67,1:22:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將你約出來的龜田先生加以殺害
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:02.97,1:22:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再將他的屍體藏到
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:04.17,1:22:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,位於船尾的箱子裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:06.47,1:22:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在機房裡殺人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:08.27,1:22:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:09.27,1:22:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行兇時留下的血跡 空彈殼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:11.87,1:22:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有 他把龜田先生約出來的信紙
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:13.97,1:22:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都在機房裡找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:15.97,1:22:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想那封信恐怕直接就放在房門底下吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:19.87,1:22:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後 鯨井先生回到餐廳以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:22.77,1:22:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,估算組長已經放棄了再找叶才三的念頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:26.87,1:22:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就找蟹江私下談話
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:28.87,1:22:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地點應該就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:30.37,1:22:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,餐廳旁邊的廁所吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:32.87,1:22:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你早先一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:34.57,1:22:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就用什麼藥先讓蟹江睡著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:37.97,1:22:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後 你剝了他的衣服和手錶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:40.07,1:22:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把這些套在龜田先生身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:43.27,1:22:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後再設下香煙的機關
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:45.07,1:22:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:45.87,1:22:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你之所以大叫出聲引起船員們注意的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:49.57,1:22:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不但是為了讓他們目擊到當時放置屍體的箱子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:52.37,1:22:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有起火燃燒之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:53.97,1:22:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是為了強調你是被人找到甲板上來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:58.37,1:23:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那張被你丟在廁所垃圾桶裡的便條紙
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:01.87,1:23:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道署名是叶才三之後假裝很震驚
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:04.17,1:23:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好讓蟹江自己主動接近你都是為了達成你的計畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:09.07,1:23:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你在事後一定會說
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:10.17,1:23:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那張便條紙是夾在紙火柴之類的藉口吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:15.17,1:23:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你之所以會設計讓自己被人找了出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:17.47,1:23:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為的就是要一切看來都
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:20.07,1:23:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出自於蟹江之手
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:21.57,1:23:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至於你在甲板上的旗子上
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:23.57,1:23:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黏上香煙的時間呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:25.77,1:23:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在你為屍體穿上衣服之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:28.57,1:23:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這麼一來
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:29.87,1:23:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家在聽到槍聲之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:31.47,1:23:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕到甲板來的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:32.87,1:23:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只要讓船尾的箱子引爆
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:34.87,1:23:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能順理成章地
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:36.17,1:23:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為自己製造不在場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:41.07,1:23:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至於你什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:42.77,1:23:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將昏迷的蟹江從廁所拖到船頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:45.27,1:23:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是大家在船尾
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:46.87,1:23:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觀察那具焦屍的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:49.07,1:23:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後來 接下來這段時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:51.27,1:23:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一直在觀察我們的一舉一動
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:54.17,1:23:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓在船尾的鞭炮引爆
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:56.07,1:23:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你趁著我們聽到聲音趕過去的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:59.27,1:24:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又再度地回到船頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:01.37,1:24:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對準蟹江的太陽穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:03.27,1:24:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將他射殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:04.87,1:24:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接著呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:05.67,1:24:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又對準窗戶玻璃朝自己的手臂
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:07.57,1:24:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,往餐廳的方向射了一槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:12.37,1:24:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:14.07,1:24:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只要再做兩個香煙機關
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:15.77,1:24:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就萬事具備了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:16.97,1:24:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後 你再回到船尾
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:19.17,1:24:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謊稱你要將一切坦白出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:21.17,1:24:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引著大家在餐廳集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:23.17,1:24:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為的就是要等待鞭炮爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:26.07,1:24:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只要在第一聲槍響倒下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:28.47,1:24:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任何人都會認為是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:30.77,1:24:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人朝船頭的方向朝你開槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:33.77,1:24:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先等一下 毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:36.17,1:24:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在他倒下來之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:38.27,1:24:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上看了他的傷口
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:40.07,1:24:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他事先就受傷的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:42.27,1:24:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那血早就流得...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:43.47,1:24:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是網球搞的鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:45.17,1:24:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在朝手臂開槍之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:46.87,1:24:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就先在腋下夾了一顆網球抑制動脈的血液
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:50.27,1:24:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來就能阻止血液流出
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:52.67,1:24:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在鞭炮引爆之前他就一直夾著
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:55.67,1:24:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惜他沒有想到
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:56.87,1:25:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭竟然會在餐廳的桌子底下發現了這顆網球
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:00.87,1:25:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他趁著大家聽到第二聲槍響分心的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:04.07,1:25:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才把那顆網球抽出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:06.17,1:25:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是他在把蟹江拖到船頭的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:09.57,1:25:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不先殺了他呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:10.77,1:25:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為 發現焦屍之後蟹江就畏罪自殺的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:14.57,1:25:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個手法看起來實在是過於牽強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:18.17,1:25:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如此一來 蟹江讓屍體穿上他的衣服的手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:21.37,1:25:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就難以解釋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:23.17,1:25:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他之所以讓屍體的雙手上揚
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:25.27,1:25:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至鬆開手錶的錶帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:27.27,1:25:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是引誘我們上鉤的障眼法
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:30.17,1:25:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至於他大老遠從大阪找來服部平次這個偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:32.97,1:25:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為的也是這個目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:34.77,1:25:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鯨井先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:36.87,1:25:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真要說來
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:37.87,1:25:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你原本應該找我們來做偵探的工作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:40.77,1:25:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之所以會找大阪的偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:42.77,1:25:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為你就住在關西的關係吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:47.47,1:25:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為一般住在關東的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:49.47,1:25:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在把撲克牌放回盒子的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:51.57,1:25:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不會說擺到盒子裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:51.57,1:25:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}關東話是"放到"
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:53.87,1:25:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:55.57,1:25:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 就剩證據了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:59.07,1:26:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於這點
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:00.57,1:26:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待會只要查看一下玻璃的彈痕四周
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:05.07,1:26:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定會發現魯米諾反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:07.97,1:26:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反應也許不強
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:09.17,1:26:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過你在開槍的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:10.37,1:26:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玻璃上一定多少沾了你的血液才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:15.97,1:26:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:18.37,1:26:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是個陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:19.67,1:26:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是什麼人要害我入罪的陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:22.47,1:26:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老小子 你還想嘴硬啊你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:25.97,1:26:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚上的星星還真是漂亮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:30.07,1:26:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:32.37,1:26:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:33.67,1:26:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船的左舷怎麼會有
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:35.57,1:26:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一顆星星不斷地靠近啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:43.27,1:26:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:44.67,1:26:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,服部
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:54.47,1:26:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:55.57,1:26:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是第一個發現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:58.37,1:26:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蟹江被吊在船頭之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:59.77,1:27:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被你硬生生打到海裡的證人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:04.97,1:27:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下子 你就沒有辦法脫罪了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:08.27,1:27:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鯨井先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:10.07,1:27:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 你怎麼會知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:12.47,1:27:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蟹江不是殺人兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:14.87,1:27:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是看手錶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:16.67,1:27:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般戴在右手的手錶調整鈕都在左邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:20.47,1:27:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是焦屍上的手錶卻是戴在左手上
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:23.17,1:27:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就立刻排除蟹江是兇手的可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:26.07,1:27:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要讓死者扮成自己的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:28.17,1:27:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世上應該不會有人把手錶戴錯手才對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:32.97,1:27:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到自己兄弟過去炫耀的手錶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:35.17,1:27:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會在緊要關頭摔了你一個跟頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:37.67,1:27:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不但如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:38.47,1:27:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當初刊登這趟行程廣告的也是鯨井先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:42.37,1:27:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這恐怕是你們20年前就說好的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:44.97,1:27:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說好追訴期屆滿這天
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:46.37,1:27:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要以古川大的名字在報紙上刊登那則廣告
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:50.77,1:27:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們三個只要在這裡會合之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:53.07,1:27:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就可以從哪個秘密金庫
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:55.07,1:27:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提出你們這20年來都沒有動過的那筆贓款
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:58.77,1:28:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了提這筆錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:00.07,1:28:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當初開戶的印鑑
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:02.37,1:28:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鑰匙和簽名都缺一不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:06.17,1:28:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們每個人負責保管一樣東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:08.67,1:28:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算20年後容貌改變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:11.27,1:28:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是可以憑三樣東西來認當年的夥伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:14.27,1:28:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:15.17,1:28:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,負責簽名的鯨井先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:17.67,1:28:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上船之後 一下子就認出了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:19.97,1:28:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,負責保管印鑑和鑰匙的龜田和蟹江
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:21.87,1:28:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是當年一起行搶的兄弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:23.87,1:28:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而他的殺人計畫也就從此展開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:27.57,1:28:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:29.27,1:28:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你殺了他們之後拿到印鑑和鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:31.87,1:28:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就可以一個人獨吞那四億元了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:34.77,1:28:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是聰明反被聰明誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:36.47,1:28:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法律追訴期好不容易過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:38.77,1:28:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你卻花了這麼多的心思殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:41.77,1:28:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不服氣罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:44.77,1:28:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想設計一個完美的計畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:47.87,1:28:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把叶才三給比下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:50.17,1:28:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20年前 他根本無視我的計畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:54.27,1:28:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這麼做只是想超越
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:55.97,1:28:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個黑影計畫師
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:58.37,1:28:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:59.67,1:29:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼和那件案子相關的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:01.97,1:29:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次全都擠到船上來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:04.67,1:29:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我根本沒有在廣告上
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:05.97,1:29:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提到叶才三的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:07.87,1:29:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道你不知道「古川大」所代表的意思嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:12.07,1:29:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個名字筆劃很少又很容易記
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:15.87,1:29:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叶才三有的時候才會拿它來作代替的名字用
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:19.47,1:29:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般人應該不知道這個名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:22.97,1:29:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是有趣極了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:25.07,1:29:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把古川大橫放過來看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:28.37,1:29:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不就變成了才三叶了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:32.67,1:29:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼看法律追訴期就要到期了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:35.47,1:29:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是因為這樣才過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:38.07,1:29:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是半信半疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:40.87,1:29:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說「古川大」
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:42.47,1:29:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本就是叶才三遊戲人間給自己取的假名
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:46.07,1:29:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:49.17,1:29:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就沒有辦法跟他相比
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:53.07,1:29:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為 你這20年來
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:56.17,1:30:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還被叶才三玩弄於股掌之間而不自知
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:33.67,1:31:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 你掉進海裡了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:36.37,1:31:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:37.47,1:31:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:38.67,1:31:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被他從身後一推就掉進海裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:41.37,1:31:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們沒有發現我失蹤啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:43.57,1:31:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太無情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:45.17,1:31:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 你得救太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:47.87,1:31:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我飄在大海裡的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:49.57,1:31:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那個漁夫大叔把我撈起來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:52.67,1:31:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時我可憐死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:54.37,1:31:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不但得在海裡面脫掉衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:56.07,1:31:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還要拼命用手電筒向遠處的漁船打信號
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:58.77,1:32:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們竟然都不擔心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:00.97,1:32:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你 都脫光了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:02.97,1:32:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這還用說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:04.27,1:32:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你穿那種衣服試試看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:05.77,1:32:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吸了水之後重得要命
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:07.37,1:32:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弄不好 還會多一條冤魂呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:10.77,1:32:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一沒脫的 就只有這條短褲
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:13.67,1:32:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟一個不知道什麼時候塞進我口袋裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:17.97,1:32:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個護身符而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:20.87,1:32:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:22.07,1:32:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道這種東西有沒有用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:29.27,1:32:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:30.47,1:32:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:31.87,1:32:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用裝了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:33.47,1:32:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到和葉送的護身符
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:35.27,1:32:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都不知道魂到哪兒去了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:36.77,1:32:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是不是 我剛才還在想
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:39.47,1:32:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種不吉利的護身符還是丟掉的好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:41.17,1:32:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:41.87,1:32:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想因為這樣遭到天譴
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:43.67,1:32:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是留著好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:46.07,1:32:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你就別忘了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:01.87,1:33:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自首的人有三個
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:05.47,1:33:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是共犯啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:07.77,1:33:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死了一個人 自首的人卻有三個
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:11.57,1:33:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是挺有趣的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:14.37,1:33:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:15.77,1:33:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被殺了四次的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:20.57,1:33:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:22.77,1:33:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鐵頭功
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:24.87,1:33:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下回的案件超特別
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:26.37,1:33:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年糕燒好了 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:27.97,1:33:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了 今年也請多指教
